      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="my-12 md:my-24">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">/ about me</h2>
      <p class="text-md md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm a web developer and an actress, passionate about learning new skills and creating software to make the world a better place. I am a curious person and a fast learner; hard work doesn't scare me. My goal is to create things that make a difference.
